OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Jess Jonassen to Pooja Vastrakar, WICKET Pooja Vastrakar run out Jess Jonassen (India Women 277 Runs for 7 wickets). Good length, outside leg stump, Harmanpreet uses her feet and tries to drive this straight down the ground, Jonassen does well to stop this and completes an easy run out at the non-striker's end as Pooja Vastrakar is halfway down the pitch for the run. India end their innings on 277 after fifties from Mithali Raj, Yastika Bhatia and Harmanpreet Kaur. Stay tuned for the chase!
